               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> What time did you miss them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About half-past eight o'clock—you had left about ten minutes past eight—I saw you with a pair of shoes in your hand, but you were not then going out—I could not swear that they were my shoes.</p>
